      <title>德意志银行的DWS Moves Star Star租用Kelly失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-14/dws-moves-star-hire-kelly-off-management-role-as-ceo-takes-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DWS集团替代方案负责人保罗·凯利（Paul Kelly）仅仅两年后负责德意志银行AG投资部门的关键部门后，就脱颖而出。]]></description>
